{"tid":1772104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"無人係condom 美眾院通過維吾爾法案 哈薩克人籲不要忘記他們","createTime":"2019-12-06T10:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T18:50:13.000Z","uid":165683,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"853db5a825d15ef69678f58fc4638a5d59aca223","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"美國國會眾議院3日通過《維吾爾人權政策法案》後，哈薩克人權組織呼籲國際社會，不要忘記哈薩克人在新疆也同樣遭受迫害。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦眾議院3日晚間投票，以407票同意、1票反對的壓倒性比數，通過《維吾爾人權政策法案》。<br />\n<br />\n哈薩克人權組織（Atajurt Kazakh Human Rights）負責人別克紮提（Bekzat Mahsutkhan）呼籲，希望世界別忘記哈薩克人遭遇的人權迫害。<br />\n<br />\n別克紮提說：「（通過法律）我們很高興的，但是作為一個哈薩克人，一個哈薩克人代表，我們很擔心，我們哈薩克人的利益，能不能獲得保障。」<br />\n<br />\n他呼籲美國國會，應該考慮起草並通過「哈薩克人權政策法案」。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國官方資料，在新疆維吾爾族自治區約有1千多萬維吾爾人，占當地總人口數近半，另外約有150萬哈薩克人。和維吾爾人一樣，也有不少哈薩克人被關押在新疆再教育營。<br />\n<br />\n根據自由亞洲電台報導，新疆近日開展了自2017年以來，第三次大規模查扣哈薩克文書籍的行動，主要針對學校及圖書館。新疆伊犁哈薩克族自治州多所學校自上周起，強逼學生交出哈薩克文讀物。當局的目的是禁止哈族學生學習哈薩克文，只能學習中國政府編寫的歷史和哈族人傳統文化知識。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2043859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2043859&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrufsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=28005623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2043859</a>"},{"pid":"ff06c56069ea2eaff7cd3b7df1e7d381e912f70c","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"461d9a4ca407f173f36ad14c2f75a9a4605cd534","tid":1772104,"uid":95610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adf35bf914346aa491f180ed930e4bf0584916e","tid":1772104,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"其實包埋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/178/text\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F178%2Ftext&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrufsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=c05883c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/178/text</a><br />\nAn Act to condemn gross human rights violations of <span style=\"color: red;\">ethnic Turkic Muslims</span> in Xinjiang, and calling for an end to arbitrary detention, torture, and harassment of these communities inside and outside China."},{"pid":"7efbe0ba4470c38320d17cba020459e08606ad41","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72e31f45bc4903d6784946e9f561ca2a171b365a","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3adf35bf914346aa491f180ed930e4bf0584916e","tid":1772104,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"其實包埋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/178/text\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F178%2Ftext&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrufsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=c05883c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/178/text</a><br />\nAn Act to condemn gross human rights violations of <span style=\"color: red;\">ethnic Turkic Muslims</span> in Xinjiang, and calling for an end to arbitrary detention, torture, and harassment of these communities inside and outside China."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"哈薩克本土都有"},{"pid":"d5095966a9acf4cb8e716f154f69921115571a0d","tid":1772104,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342c3eb3b733baea75aa865c09faf237b86d7fdd","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190922/60070985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F60070985&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrufsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=9ea965ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F60070985&h=d40d030a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190922/60070985</a><br />\n<br />\n【反華示威】反對中國經濟擴張 哈薩克兩市爆示威<br />\n<br />\n中亞國家哈薩克周六有示威，抗議中國經濟擴張以及仍然大權在握的前總統納扎爾巴耶夫（Nursultan Nazarbayev）。<br />\n在最大城市阿拉木圖市中心，數十人高喊反中國擴張和「老人，滾蛋」口號後被迅速押上車帶走。內政部表示，在阿拉木圖和首都努爾蘇丹，共57人因參與未經批准的示威而被扣留。該部發表聲明，指有市民漠視檢察署的屢次警告，響應一個「被取締極端組織」的號召參與示威。所指的被取締極端組織，是「哈薩克民主選擇黨」（DCK）。"},{"pid":"5129a4d42e2b863de57ea822c2e0e6b7e989a1a2","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"有個哈薩克人手足被補無得保釋，無人講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eBBOvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eBBOvS</a>"},{"pid":"6ebfe196efb4ee1c09be58c5d0bd4764370ce10f","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"[929 前奏] 哈薩克兩大城市爆發反中示威 數十人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/edfhES\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/edfhES</a>"},{"pid":"abe56cecc646fb167e74379c52f02f2e511378b7","tid":1772104,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"哈薩克斯坦學生 油麻地管有汽油彈被拘捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740721\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740721</a>"},{"pid":"610ffd18ef26ff51a4189cc1c3ca3bcc4360d81c","tid":1772104,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":